data.description: Gorgeous townhome in River Oaks, in excellent condition! New Paint, New Carpet, upgraded kitchen with 42" cabinets, gleaming granite counter tops, hardwood floors, custom wine rack and back splash! Large bedrooms upstairs with 2 full baths. Large deck, Walkout basement, full bath and 3rd bedroom in basement. Full size washer & dryer side by side.  Priced to sell quickly. Fully finished walk out basement. Onsite pool & fitness and minutes from shops & dining, Quantico, Fort Belvoir.  Commuter lot less than 10 minutes away!
